fulltitle: Jimmy Heath:  My Mentor, Dizzy Gillespie
description: Jimmy Heath - Dizzy Gillespie, My Mentor. Answering questions from the young musicians of the Tucson Jazz Institute Ellington Band, Jimmy Heath remembers his mentor. An excerpt from "Passing the Torch." To view on Amazon Prime:  https://www.amazon.com/Passing-Torch-Jimmy-Heath/dp/B071LFRQDF/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1499727832&sr=8-1&
